:"2019-02-28T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"岩牙我地利記終於等到了"},{"pid":"8ae3835ad8a3377d414288a7bdab89069d7a95f7","tid":1040773,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"我叫你柒頭熱"},{"pid":"3c5e84faadcd507323d6827336dc8d3bb866a4af","tid":1040773,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ec071dcc148f8cb386143fe4f4938ba7fbe4be","tid":1040773,"uid":43861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b3e08580d0c2d928493d31e32f8a71716161af7","tid":1040773,"uid":7916,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"有未來驚乜春<br />\n未來一定會奪冠"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"岩牙我地利記終於等到了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"利記有歐聯"},{"pid":"f354398aef8409cfbcebf2437942caaacc9b3a5b","tid":1040773,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"未來熱 可以改名叫做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十年熱</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f7de093a1472f1dc285df54b0a8279e8990e8e9","tid":1040773,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"亞當斯：英格蘭不該重用熱刺球員<br />\n<br />\n據《太陽報》報導，東尼-亞當斯表示熱刺球員缺乏贏家心態，這將會影響到英格蘭在世界盃中的表現。<br />\n<br />\n作為96年歐國盃的英格蘭隊長，亞當斯相信修夫基不應該在世界盃中重用熱刺球員，因為他擔心在球會缺乏成功的經歷會讓他們在國家隊碌碌無為。"},{"pid":"d85c31c529f28d15d019153cbb0f0ebbe0e02139","tid":1040773,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"幾多屆奪冠 未來熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24817bbcbf07f89b9650058bc45761bd7bdef440","tid":1040773,"uid":40940,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"960b0921f5450a77cb71acfe930ebe476b8ce4d4","tid":1040773,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差d咩... 咁多年其實都出唔少星 但咩冠都冇個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，假切X聯XX士同熱刺同一班球員水平，同一個領隊，所有人100%狀態又無內亂<br />\n<br />\n當打得唔好時，指一指牆上班名叔，指一指心口個章，諗下過去既豐功偉績，大家都明著得呢件衫就係要贏，係傳統，呢間球會就係歸宿可以獲得成功<br />\n<br />\n熱刺呢，傳統就係強隊私家雞，關鍵時刻走樣，劣勢就崩盤，空既獎盃櫃，好似無乜成就既名叔，想名成利就就要轉會, put pressure on望未來。激勵就係咁抽象，有信念就有力量到咬住落去，望住件波衫望住個球場激唔激勵到自己。關鍵時刻含撚係死症<br />\n<br />\n差既野唔直接關人腳事，係球會既傳統"},{"pid":"a47817e633e0ad26f2242afba28a887c514a4182","tid":1040773,"uid":149427,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"97ec071dcc148f8cb386143fe4f4938ba7fbe4be","tid":1040773,"uid":43861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b3e08580d0c2d928493d31e32f8a71716161af7","tid":1040773,"uid":7916,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"有未來驚乜春<br />\n未來一定會奪冠"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"岩牙我地利記終於等到了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"好撚柒 想拉人落水又唔諗下自己咩料先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}